Package: server-suite
Version: 2.0.0
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.8), python3-pip, ufw, fail2ban, docker.io, curl
Maintainer: Server Suite Team <dev@example.com>
Description: Self-hosted server automation and management suite
 Server Suite provides idempotent installation and management of
 common self-hosted services including web servers, databases,
 file storage, and monitoring. Version 2.0 adds encrypted secrets,
 drift detection, remote execution, and TPM integration.